name: Unemployment rate
description: Seasonally adjusted U.S. civilian unemployment rate for workers age 16 and over

name: Nonfarm payroll employment
description: Total number of employees on nonfarm payrolls in the U.S. economy

name: CPI all items
description: Consumer Price Index for all urban consumers for all items in the U.S.

name: PCE price index
description: Personal Consumption Expenditures price index for all items

name: Real GDP
description: Inflation adjusted gross domestic product for the United States

name: ISM manufacturing PMI
description: Institute for Supply Management manufacturing purchasing managers index (headline)

name: Real retail sales
description: Inflation adjusted retail and food services sales

name: Industrial production
description: Index of real output of all manufacturing
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: Consumer sentiment index
description: University of Michigan index of consumer sentiment for U.S. households
source: University of Michigan, Survey Research Center

name: Housing starts total
description: Total new privately owned housing units started

name: Building permits total
description: Total new privately owned housing units authorized by building permits

name: Housing completions total
description: Total new privately owned housing units completed

name: New single family home sales
description: Number of new one family houses sold at a seasonally adjusted annual rate
source: U.S. Census Bureau and U.S. Department of Housing and Urban Development

name: Existing home sales total
description: Total existing single family homes and condos sold at a seasonally adjusted annual rate

name: Existing home inventory
description: Number of existing homes available for sale in the U.S. housing market

name: Existing home months supply
description: Months supply of existing homes for sale at the current sales pace

name: FHFA HPI U.S. purchase only
description: FHFA national house price index for purchase only transactions

name: FHFA HPI U.S. all transactions
description: FHFA national house price index including purchase and refinance appraisals

name: S&P Case Shiller U.S. national HPI
description: S&P CoreLogic Case Shiller U.S. national home price index (non seasonally adjusted)

name: Mortgage delinquency rate
description: Delinquency rate on single family residential mortgages booked in domestic offices of commercial banks
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: 30 year fixed mortgage rate
description: Freddie Mac primary mortgage market survey 30 year fixed rate for conforming loans

name: 15 year fixed mortgage rate
description: Freddie Mac primary mortgage market survey 15 year fixed rate for conforming loans

name: 5-1 ARM mortgage rate
description: Freddie Mac primary mortgage market survey 5 year adjustable rate mortgage (5-1 ARM) rate

name: Fed funds target upper bound
description: Upper limit of the Federal Open Market Committee target range for the federal funds rate
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: Fed funds target lower bound
description: Lower limit of the Federal Open Market Committee target range for the federal funds rate
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: Effective fed funds rate
description: Daily effective federal funds rate based on overnight unsecured lending between depository institutions
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: SOFR
description: Secured Overnight Financing Rate based on overnight Treasury repurchase transactions
source: Federal Reserve Bank of New York / Office of Financial Research

name: Fed total assets
description: Total assets held by the Federal Reserve on its consolidated balance sheet
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: Fed SOMA MBS holdings (Wednesday)
description: Face value of mortgage backed securities held by the Federal Reserve System on Wednesday
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: Fed SOMA MBS holdings (weekly average)
description: Weekly average face value of mortgage backed securities held by the Federal Reserve System
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: 2 year Treasury yield
description: Daily constant maturity yield on 2 year U.S. Treasury securities
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: 5 year Treasury yield
description: Daily constant maturity yield on 5 year U.S. Treasury securities
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: 10 year Treasury yield
description: Daily constant maturity yield on 10 year U.S. Treasury securities
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: 30 year Treasury yield
description: Daily constant maturity yield on 30 year U.S. Treasury securities
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: 10 year TIPS real yield
description: Daily real yield on 10 year Treasury Inflation Protected Securities

name: 10 year breakeven inflation rate
description: Difference between nominal 10 year Treasury yield and 10 year TIPS yield used as the 10 year inflation compensation
source: Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis

name: 5 year interest rate swap rate (discontinued)
description: Constant maturity 5 year fixed for floating U.S. dollar interest rate swap rate (historical series - discontinued)
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)

name: 10 year interest rate swap rate (discontinued)
description: Constant maturity 10 year fixed for floating U.S. dollar interest rate swap rate (historical series - discontinued)
source: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System (US)
